@startuml MyAIStorybook_SSD_Character_Chat
title MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Character Chat Scenario

actor "User" as User
participant ":System" as System

note over User, System
    Character Chat Scenario (Main Success)
    System is treated as BLACK BOX
end note

User -> System : selectStory(story_id)
System --> User : story_details

User -> System : selectCharacter(character_name)
System --> User : chat_ready

loop [conversation continues]
    User -> System : sendMessage(message_text)
    System --> User : character_response(response_text)
end

User -> System : endChat()
System --> User : chat_ended

note right of System
    System operations are high-level
    Character responses generated internally
    Focus on WHAT system does
end note

@enduml
